    "style": "Heading 1",
    "text": "四、技术架构",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Heading 2",
    "text": "4.1 后端技术栈",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "• Web 框架：Flask 3.x（工厂函数 + 蓝图模块化架构）",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "• 数据库：MySQL 8.0（utf8mb4_unicode_ci 字符集）",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "• ORM：Flask-SQLAlchemy（声明式模型）",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "• 认证：Flask-Login（会话管理 + 登录保护装饰器）",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "• 表单验证：Flask-WTF（CSRF 保护）",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "• 密码加密：Werkzeug generate_password_hash / check_password_hash",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "• 蓝图划分：main / auth / game / score / admin / item（6个蓝图）",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Heading 2",
    "text": "4.2 前端技术栈",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "• 页面模板：Jinja2（继承自 base.html，统一绿色森林主题）",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "• 游戏渲染：HTML5 Canvas 2D（纯原生，无外部游戏框架）",
    "has_image": false,
    "images": []
  },
  {
    "style": "Normal",
    "text": "• 游戏架构：模块化 JavaScript（9个独立模块，全局命名空间通信）",
